title: ‘Beverly Hills’ Episode 17 and ‘Dubai’ Episode 14
description:
Rachel kicks off this week’s 'Morally Corrupt' by breaking down all of our recent Bravo news with Callie Curry (1:08), before Rachel and Callie move on to discuss Season 1 ‘The Real Housewives of Dubai’ Reunion Part 2 (28:35). Rachel is then joined by Jodi Walker to chat about Season 12, Episode 17 of ‘The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills’ (40:00).
Host: Rachel Lindsay
Guests: Callie Curry and Jodi Walker
Producers: Devon Manze
Theme Song: Devon Renaldo
